  "remarks": "Olga Ayziman is the ex-wife of Mikhail Fridman, founder and one of the main shareholders of the Alfa Group, which includes the major Russian bank Alfa Bank, considered as a top Russian financier and enabler of President Vladimir Putin’s inner circle. Mikhail Fridman is the major sponsor of his ex-wife’s activities and needs since she moved to Paris.",
